## Preparation
### Install required tools
sudo apt install --no-install-recommends build-essential xz-utils wget python3-distutils

## Run The Script
### Set the openwrt version inside the script

* edit bin/[device].sh
* change the OPENWRT_VERSION value
* ./bin/[device].sh

### Set the openwrt version from system environment

* export OPENWRT_VERSION=xx.xx.x
* ./bin/[device.sh]
* unset OPENWRT_VERSION

## Output
if build success, the binary files is located in working directory

- [device]_[openwrt_version]_recovery.bin
- [device]_[openwrt_version]_sysupgrade.bin
